#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn55.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Rājakārāmavagga "
msgstr "2. A Thousand Nuns "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Tatiyadevacārikasutta "
msgstr "20. A Visit to the Gods (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.368, sc1
msgctxt "sn55.20:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā—seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—jetavane antarahito devesu tāvatiṃsesu pāturahosi. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, vanished from Jeta’s Grove and reappeared among the gods of the Thirty-Three. "

msgctxt "sn55.20:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā tāvatiṃsakāyikā devatāyo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho tā devatāyo bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then several deities of the company of the Thirty-Three went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood to one side. The Buddha said to them: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn55.20:2.1"
msgid "“Sādhu kho, āvuso, buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgamanaṃ hoti—"
msgstr "“Reverends, it’s good to have experiential confidence in the Buddha. … "

msgctxt "sn55.20:2.2"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.20:2.3"
msgid "Buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgamanahetu kho, āvuso, evam’idhekacce sattā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā. "
msgstr "It’s the reason why some sentient beings are stream-enterers, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

msgctxt "sn55.20:2.4"
msgid "Sādhu kho, āvuso, dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "It’s good to have experiential confidence in the teaching. … "

msgctxt "sn55.20:2.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.20:2.6"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgamanaṃ hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "and to have the ethical conduct that’s loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.20:2.7"
msgid "Ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgamanahetu kho, āvuso, evam’idhekacce sattā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā”ti. "
msgstr "It’s the reason why some sentient beings are stream-enterers, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn55.20:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu kho, mārisa, buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgamanaṃ hoti—"
msgstr "“Good sir, it’s good to have experiential confidence in the Buddha … "

msgctxt "sn55.20:3.2"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn55.20:3.3"
msgid "Buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgamanahetu kho, mārisa, evamayaṃ pajā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā. "
msgstr "It’s the reason why some sentient beings are stream-enterers, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening. "

msgctxt "sn55.20:3.4"
msgid "Sādhu kho, mārisa, dhamme … pe … "
msgstr "It’s good to have experiential confidence in the teaching. … "

msgctxt "sn55.20:3.5"
msgid "saṅghe … pe … "
msgstr "the Saṅgha … "

msgctxt "sn55.20:3.6"
msgid "ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgamanaṃ hoti akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi. "
msgstr "and to have the ethical conduct that’s loved by the noble ones … leading to immersion. "

msgctxt "sn55.20:3.7"
msgid "Ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgamanahetu kho, mārisa, evamayaṃ pajā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyaṇā”ti. "
msgstr "It’s the reason why some sentient beings are stream-enterers, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.20:3.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.20:3.9"
msgid "Rājakārāmavaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn55.20:4.1"
msgid "Sahassabrāhmaṇānanda, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.20:4.2"
msgid "duggati apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.20:4.3"
msgid "Mittāmaccā duve vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn55.20:4.4"
msgid "tayo ca devacārikāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
